# Testes API (dnd-api)

1. Skills globais `jest` + `testing`; overlay `nestjs-api-tests`.
2. Catalog: `*.queries.spec.ts` + `*.e2e-spec.ts`
3. Game: `*.application.spec.ts` + `*.e2e-spec.ts`
4. Meta: **≥ 80%** lines em `catalog/**/queries/` e `*.mapper.ts`
5. E2E: GET 200 lista, GET 200 slug (`fighter`), GET 404
6. `npm run test:cov` antes de PR
